text:
Some other great options for the sections that would elevate the CMS builder from "good" to "great" would be:
1. Responsive padding/margin options (like a phone, tablet and desktop selector);
2. Field to add an ID (useful for jump-to links);
3. Custom classes (already mentioned);
4. Responsive column direction (flex row reverse)
5. Video backgrounds (with support for locally hosted videos &amp; youtube, vimeo, etc);
6. Also border and drop shadow options, already mentioned would be cool too.
Cheers, you guys have been doing great work!
